+ I ThisWindow (Maximized) Maximize toggle
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I Maximize Forget
+ I Raise
+ I Maximize $0 $1
+ I Move $2 $3
+ I Focus

DestroyFunc 	NextWindow
